Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.52,0:00:19.45,Ange-internal/narrator,Sylvia,0000,0000,0000,,She won't come back, will she?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.32,0:00:24.08,Ange-internal/narrator,Sylvia,0000,0000,0000,,I did the right thing, didn't I, Onii-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:28.79,Ange-main,Riza,0000,0000,0000,,Poor Julio.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.98,0:00:31.76,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:37.01,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't believe I couldn't \Ndispose of that bad Norma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.71,0:00:40.58,Ange-main,Riza,0000,0000,0000,,You did well, Julio.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:43.18,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Did I do well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:45.01,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.01,0:00:49.06,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Mother would never praise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.58,0:00:52.50,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,She kept favoring Angelise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.21,0:00:55.81,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,She died defending Angelise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.78,0:01:03.94,Ange-main,Sylvia,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.57,0:01:07.65,Ange-main,Riza,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's Mama's turn to ask for a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.99,0:01:09.67,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:12.38,Ange-main,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to open the \Nsingular point, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:14.29,Ange-main,Riza,0000,0000,0000,,Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:19.22,Ange-main,Sylvia,0000,0000,0000,,Guard Chief, what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.67,0:01:20.62,Ange-main,Riza,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.15,0:01:23.02,Ange-main,Sylvia,0000,0000,0000,,Someone help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:27.06,Ange-main,Sylvia,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:31.32,Ange-main,Sylvia,0000,0000,0000,,Help! Angelise-oneesama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:06.44,Ange-EpTitle,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(504,463)}Dragon Song
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:04.62,Ange-top,Vivian,0000,0000,0000,,A shift change?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:06.45,Ange-top,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,First Troop has been relegated to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:09.08,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,backup, due to concerns about our readiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:11.85,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Eleanor Squad is on deck today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:13.53,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, it'll be Betty Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:18.42,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,Well, combat's out of the \Nquestion with only five of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:21.23,Ange-main,Rosalie,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so nonchalant about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.23,0:03:23.65,Ange-main,Rosalie,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't get deployed, we don't get paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:24.68,Ange-main,Rosalie,0000,0000,0000,,Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:27.74,Ange-main,Rosalie,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot, Breakout Sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:29.30,Ange-main,Chris,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they never come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:31.88,Ange-main,Rosalie,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:36.11,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,Please, give this to Angelise-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:39.39,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she's getting proper meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.39,0:03:41.03,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:43.78,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:46.52,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I can think of it as a diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:49.65,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that, I want to take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:51.08,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,How many days has it been?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:52.29,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,A week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:54.67,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder you smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:56.75,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,You smell the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:04:01.67,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I don't ask for much.\NJust some water to bathe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:07.43,Ange-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's Salia-oneesama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.05,0:04:10.64,Ange-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Salute Salia-oneesama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:12.15,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:16.54,Ange-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,She's so pretty and awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:19.48,Ange-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally going to join First Troop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:22.02,Ange-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be like Salia-oneesama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:26.91,Ange-flashback,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be like you, Onee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:36.99,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Here, for Onee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:40.12,Ange-main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for doing this every year, Salia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:46.05,Ange-main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:49.43,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,The Youth Group girls called me Onee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:52.14,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Am I that old already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:54.31,Ange-main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You're only seventeen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:56.20,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm {\i1}already{\i0} seventeen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:05:01.53,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the same age as Alektra.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:06.16,Ange-flashback,Jasmine,0000,0000,0000,,Alektra!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:12.89,Ange-flashback,Jasmine,0000,0000,0000,,Maggie, analgesics!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:14.37,Ange-flashback,Jasmine,0000,0000,0000,,Bring all the bandages you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.57,0:05:17.04,Ange-flashback,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,That's Onee-sama's machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.59,0:05:20.24,Ange-flashback,Jasmine,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Alektra.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:21.39,Ange-flashback,Jasmine,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:24.47,Ange-flashback,Alektra,0000,0000,0000,,They're, they're all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:29.30,Ange-flashback,Alektra,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Fei-Ling has a message for Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:35.44,Ange-flashback,Alektra,0000,0000,0000,,The family heirloom is hidden under \Nthe bottom of the third drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.44,0:05:37.31,Ange-flashback,Jasmine,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! You can deal with that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:40.71,Ange-flashback,Alektra,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Jasmine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:42.94,Ange-flashback,Alektra,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:50.77,Ange-flashback,Alektra,0000,0000,0000,,Fei-Ling, Vanessa, the knight's family...\N They're all dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:56.32,Ange-flashback,Alektra,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't handle the Villkiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:58.44,Ange-flashback,Alektra,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:00.01,Ange-flashback,Jasmine,0000,0000,0000,,Alektra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:01.29,Ange-flashback,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:06.96,Ange-flashback,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Alektra is strong, beautiful, and awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:08.55,Ange-flashback,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,You're good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:10.56,Ange-flashback,Jasmine,0000,0000,0000,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:13.60,Ange-flashback,Alektra,0000,0000,0000,,Salia, of the Primary Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:15.23,Ange-flashback,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of DRAGON was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.23,0:06:16.21,Ange-flashback,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,How big was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:17.22,Ange-flashback,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,How tough?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:19.71,Ange-flashback,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:24.57,Ange-flashback,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive it for doing this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:30.45,Ange-flashback,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,I'll avenge you, Alektra!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:34.27,Ange-flashback,Alektra,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Salia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:39.42,Ange-main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:42.79,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped. You were only three.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:46.13,Ange-main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,But the family's duty, my sister's wishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:48.22,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've inherited them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:53.72,Ange-main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,As an armorsmith, I'm going to \Nfree the world with the Villkiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.45,Ange-main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,For my sister, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:07:00.51,Ange-main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,And as a rider, you can do the \Nsame for Alek— I mean, Jill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:02.00,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.39,0:07:07.57,Ange-flashback,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:08.78,Ange-flashback,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:11.41,Ange-flashback,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:12.68,Ange-flashback,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Even more than now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:13.67,Ange-flashback,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:17.87,Ange-flashback,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard you try,\N if you can't do it, you can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:19.97,Ange-flashback,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:22.02,Ange-flashback,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't understand that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.41,0:07:25.50,Ange-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,you end up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:29.67,Ange-flashback,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,What is it that I'm lacking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:34.62,Ange-flashback,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,That {\i1}we're{\i0} lacking, you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:40.87,Ange-internal/narrator,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,Then what does Ange have?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:46.77,Ange-internal/narrator,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not giving her the Villkiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:53.32,Ange-main,Hikaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, isn't this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.19,0:07:55.56,Ange-main,Pamela,0000,0000,0000,,It's a singular signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.56,0:07:56.50,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,Location?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:07:58.24,Ange-main,Pamela,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:08:00.50,Ange-main,Pamela,0000,0000,0000,,...right above Arzenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:10.45,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,More enemies inbound.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:13.63,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Scuna class, six. No, 21.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:14.72,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Sixty-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:16.08,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,128.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:19.14,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Too many to estimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:21.85,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't even get a call. How?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.97,0:08:24.20,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,This is Commander Jill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:25.85,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,All units, listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:28.40,Ange-announcer,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ordering Battle Mode, Type 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:31.12,Ange-announcer,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,A singular point has opened above the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:31.49,Ange-main,Vivian,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:33.87,Ange-announcer,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,A massive number of DRAGONs are descending.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.27,0:08:37.62,Ange-announcer,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,Second and Third Para-mail Troops,\N deploy all units.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:40.28,Ange-announcer,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare for close-quarters combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.28,0:08:42.83,Ange-announcer,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,You are authorized to use anti-air weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:44.48,Ange-announcer,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy the DRAGONs
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:45.83,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,at all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:50.75,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Who's going to defend the base \Nif we deploy all the Para-mails?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:07.37,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:20.51,Ange-main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Die, bad guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.01,Ange-main,Pamela,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, the communicator and radar...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:38.68,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,We hereby abandon the command center.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:41.91,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,Further communications will be \Nissued from emergency command.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.10,Ange-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:51.01,Ange-main,Chris,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we got most of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:53.46,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Eleanor Squad and Betty Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:56.35,Ange-main,Rosalie,0000,0000,0000,,They took our earnings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:06.83,Ange-main,Vivian,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? They're fleeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:09.25,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Singing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:28.88,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,A Para-mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.41,0:10:32.77,Ange-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? Where's that machine from?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.62,0:11:11.05,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:12.76,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:29.53,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,Angelise-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:31.21,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,Please say something if you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:32.88,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Momoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:34.40,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,Open.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:36.42,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Momoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:38.35,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:41.87,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Momoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:44.00,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:46.01,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:48.39,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Just after we finally got back...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:51.23,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,We'll find out if we go to the Para-mails.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.45,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:54.04,Ange-main,Momoka,0000,0000,0000,,But first take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:55.58,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:57.44,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:11:59.57,Ange-main,Hikaru,0000,0000,0000,,Second Troop, annihilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:02.11,Ange-main,Olivier,0000,0000,0000,,Third Troop, four units lost \Nother than the Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:06.03,Ange-main,Olivier,0000,0000,0000,,Give all command authority \Nto Salia of First Troop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:09.93,Ange-main,Olivier,0000,0000,0000,,Instruct all the remaining \NPara-mail to attack the DRAGONs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:10.54,Ange-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:12.96,Ange-announcer,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,You heard it, Salia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:16.74,Ange-announcer,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,And return Ange to the squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:20.28,Ange-announcer,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,Only the Villkiss can stop that machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.69,0:12:21.97,Ange-announcer,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,Put Ange in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:25.67,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll deploy in the Villkiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:26.42,Ange-announcer,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:28.72,Ange-announcer,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,Follow your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:33.77,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Am I not good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:39.02,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to be useful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:42.03,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,I've worked so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:44.45,Ange-announcer,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,And it's still Ange?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:49.79,Ange-announcer,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Ange's kind of good at piloting,\N and she's a bit clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:52.39,Ange-announcer,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,But she violated orders, and she deserted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:54.14,Ange-announcer,,0000,0000,0000,,She's in detention.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:55.71,Ange-announcer,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,And it's still Ange?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:57.42,Ange-announcer,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:00.63,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'm stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:03.22,Ange-main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Salia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:12.27,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, fall back to resupply.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:17.15,Ange-main,Vivian,0000,0000,0000,,We've got this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:18.23,Ange-announcer,A,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:21.06,Ange-main,Pamela,0000,0000,0000,,First Troop deployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:21.95,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:27.00,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,Ange, your target is that \Nunidentified machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:30.48,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,It's equipped with an \Nunknown high-yield weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:31.60,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:34.00,Ange-announcer,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Jill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.07,0:13:35.90,Ange-announcer,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,Salia?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:37.71,Ange-announcer,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Salia?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:38.58,Ange-announcer,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,Return to base!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.97,0:13:40.32,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,You're violating orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:41.75,Ange-announcer,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:44.42,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it, so I'm going to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:46.88,Ange-flashback,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to defeat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:49.80,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do it for Alektra.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.98,0:13:51.97,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.26,0:13:56.33,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,They're not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:13:57.20,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:58.81,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Did they get wiped out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:01.23,Ange-main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's Salia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:30.34,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,More.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:31.87,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:33.08,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you fly faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:36.15,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:45.28,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,Salia-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:51.79,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:54.31,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,The Villkiss has to have more power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:14:58.87,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Ange was more—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:06.25,Ange-announcer,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, my chest! I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:08.08,Ange-announcer,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,It's cramped. Deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:09.99,Ange-main,Vivian,0000,0000,0000,,Ange!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:10.80,Ange-main,Ersha,0000,0000,0000,,Hilda-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:15.33,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Salia, give me back my machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.37,0:15:19.06,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:21.27,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,It's my Villkiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:35.42,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,You must think I'm stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:39.04,Ange-flashback,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,Only Ange and the Villkiss \Ncan stop that machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:45.13,Ange-flashback,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Ange's kind of good at piloting,\N and she's a bit clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:51.55,Ange-flashback,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard you try, if \Nyou can't do it, you can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:53.97,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:59.45,Ange-flashback,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,I worked harder than everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:00.26,Ange-flashback,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:08.49,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Chase her, Hilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:09.68,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:10.61,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I'll jump over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:12.37,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:15.29,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's something you'd do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:17.47,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,We're charging in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:25.88,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you move?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:31.72,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,You have to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.79,0:16:37.47,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,Or else I can't help my beloved Alektra.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:40.12,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:41.64,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Burn Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.66,0:16:51.86,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:55.96,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:57.84,Ange-main,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:16:58.33,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:00.56,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,We're past the drop threshold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:02.32,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:04.28,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:05.50,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Not for this machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:18.38,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,That was refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:22.40,Ange-announcer,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Hilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:23.80,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:25.01,Ange-announcer,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dropping her. Catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:42.33,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,I'm charging you extra, Idiot Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:45.54,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:11.32,Ange-main,Vivian,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:39.13,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,This song...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:18.02,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.82,0:19:52.79,Ange-main,Sara,0000,0000,0000,,For what reason does a false \Ncitizen sing the true Star Song?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:03.84,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,And who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.23,0:20:05.51,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,What is that song?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:30.25,Ange-main,Sara,0000,0000,0000,,The time comes, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.05,0:20:34.12,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:37.44,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is with Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.93,0:20:45.64,Ange-announcer,Pamela,0000,0000,0000,,The unidentified machine\Nand DRAGONs are retreating.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:47.82,Ange-main,Ange,0000,0000,0000,,Truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.86,0:20:50.15,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:52.33,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,The last key was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:54.28,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,...a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:01.72,Ange-internal/narrator,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,That's the real Villkiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:04.82,Ange-internal/narrator,Salia,0000,0000,0000,,Jill was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.42,0:21:08.66,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, we made it somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:13.23,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,It feels totally different from Ange.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:15.87,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:18.38,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,She was completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:22.00,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,Hilda...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:23.19,Ange-main,Hilda,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.83,0:21:24.80,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,You stink.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:31.22,Ange-main,Maggie,0000,0000,0000,,A complete disaster, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.39,0:21:34.00,Ange-main,Maggie,0000,0000,0000,,We have a bad situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:35.35,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,Worse than it already is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:37.40,Ange-main,Maggie,0000,0000,0000,,We lost the plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.04,0:21:41.98,Ange-main,Vivian,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, this is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.80,0:21:48.33,Ange-main,Vivian,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:57.97,Ange-main,Vivian,0000,0000,0000,,Ange's song was so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.24,0:22:02.48,Ange-main,Jill,0000,0000,0000,,How long do we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.79,0:22:05.10,Ange-main,Maggie,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:29.05,next episode preview,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,519)}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.01,0:23:30.58,Ange-main,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,I've been in the opening and ending,\N kept waiting for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.58,0:23:32.40,Ange-main,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,My name and identity are left unknown,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.40,0:23:34.47,Ange-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and yet I have no role next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.47,0:23:36.53,Ange-main,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an important character, am I not?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.53,0:23:39.35,Ange-top,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,So why do I have the more lines \Nin the preview than elsewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:40.94,Ange-NextEp,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(939,1)}Her Right Arm's Past
